Package model.rsa

Annotation Type Details

@Documented
@Target(METHOD)
@Retention(RUNTIME)
public @interface Details
An interface to specify the details of methods from Algorithm class. It uses enum objects to represent type of operation performed by method as well as Encoding used in them

  • Required Element Summary

    Required Elements 
    Modifier and Type Required Element Description
    java.lang.String author
    Variable that contains the author of method
    java.lang.String description
    Variable that contains the description of method

  • Optional Element Summary

    Optional Elements 
    Modifier and Type Optional Element Description
    Details.Encoding encoding
    Variable that holds the value of Encoding used in method
    Details.Operation operation
    Variable that holds the value of Operation used in method

  • Element Details

    • description

      java.lang.String description
      Variable that contains the description of method

    • author

      Variable that contains the author of method

    • encoding

    • operation

      Variable that holds the value of Operation used in method
      Default:
      model.Details.Operation.None
